    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain the <strong>tofu</strong> and pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Combine the <strong>cornflour</strong> in a large bowl with the <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong>,<strong> </strong>a small pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 75ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span><strong> cold water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>pakora batter</strong></p>",
