    {
      "instruction": "<p>Crumble the <strong>drained tofu</strong> into very small pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>crumbled tofu</strong> to the <strong>pakora batter </strong>and give everything a good mix up until fully combined, then set aside for later – this is your<strong> tofu pakora mix</strong></p>",
