    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and grate (don't chop!) the <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>green chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop roughly</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> (including the stalks) roughly</p><p>Strip the <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p>",
