    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>grated ginger</strong> and <strong>chopped green chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a <strong>food processor</strong> with the <strong>chopped coriander & mint</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>mayo</strong>, <strong>mango chutney</strong>, <strong>cider vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>chilli chutney mayo</strong></p>",
