      "instruction": "<p>Combine 1/3 of the <strong>chilli chutney mayo </strong>(save the rest for later!) with the <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix </strong>in a large bowl</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>chilli chutney slaw</strong></p>",
